Patricia Ryan (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patricia_Ryan_(actress) 0 Patricia Ryan (February 25, 1921 - February 15, 1949) was a child performer and an actress in old-time radio. She was taken ill during an evening broadcast and died the next day. Patricia_Ryan ( February_25_,_1921 - February_15_,_1949 ) was a_child_performer and an_actress in old-time_radio .
